Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈今天心情好像很坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝你怎么了 遇到什么不好的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就笑一个 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 新威尼斯正式进入了夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午练习时太阳非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳的光线就像要渗透到身体里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样我们还是要继续练习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说正是这么热的天 才是最佳的练习日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了早日成为憧憬已久的正式领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习练习～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这里是今天的一大难关哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤尾舟要通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿出大水道的时候要放开声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是运气不好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天的自我守则没能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我守则？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 爱丽丝意外地有点孩子气呢 可爱得很哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天只准成功…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天必胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:58.03,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 超级自我守则…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的自我守则是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只准踩着影子回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我守则其一 踩到没影子的地方就算输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二 任何东西的影子都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三 允许半只脚踩到阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪…这实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级幸运的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了这里就是橙色行星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的超级障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守则其一 踩到没影子的地方就算输…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天白天的曲子 你最近经常唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的自我守则是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢着石子回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩着石板的线回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是单脚跳回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 超级怯懦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向失败挑战才叫勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的自我守则也是踩着影子回家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才爱丽丝她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小后辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳着过去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下午的工作取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想来看看爱丽丝怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么样 跟平时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为爱丽丝看上去很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有看上去很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在实行自我守则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天一样 只能踩影子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…小嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要从刚才那里重来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈不准乱帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我守则其四 禁止他人帮助！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样的守则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚定下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一个人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈 你不要多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就破例像平时一样走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 没有影子的地方都是岩浆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩浆…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 爱丽丝 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说不准帮忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说了禁止他人帮助的守则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么还要做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 你去哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从见到雅典娜前辈的地方前面开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要跟过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来管我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 还是先治治自己的糊涂毛病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太简单了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为爱丽丝看上去很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才叫难度啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才能体现人生价值啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝 刚才我们见到雅典娜前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正请她指导我们练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝也快换好衣服过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈还教我们唱歌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈们 请不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是最后的超级障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…在跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又要做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么搞 搞什么搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己是正义的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的 我没有认为自己是正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为自己是爱丽丝的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就好比游戏里的隐藏角色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在危急时候遇到 会觉得幸运的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 因为是他人 所以禁止帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的守则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我守则其五 雅典娜前辈不是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很闲 接下来的练习都要好好指导我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个曲子第一次听到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 心情好像豁然开朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情…豁然开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那时…是为了我而唱这首歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜前辈无论何时 一直都是我的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 真真切切的 我不可替代的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 虽然不知道爱丽丝和雅典娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 爱丽丝的笑容看上去前所未有地自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以连一起的我都变得高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也许是因为雅典娜前辈的歌声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能感觉到 虽然只是一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝姐姐和雅典娜姐姐真是好搭档呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我明天也试试只踩着影子回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果快要失败了 灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会到地球来帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 最崭新的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:34.65,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:47.63,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:03:02.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:15.48,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.48,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:21.80,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:29.41,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:36.89,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:40.43,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:47.20,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:34.65,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:47.63,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}洒落在 舒睡的睫毛间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:03:02.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}让轻拂的风吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:15.48,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝叶间滑落的阳光 映衬你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.48,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an3}Euforia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:21.80,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}虽是个平凡无奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:29.41,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了艳丽的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:36.89,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是与你邂逅的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:40.43,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我并非孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:47.20,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因为 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:57.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}白い帽子 追いかけて笑う 響く声は高く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:09.03,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}少し早い 夏の訪れに 耳を澄ましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:16.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ゆっくりと 長くなる影ふたつ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:22.00,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな 足音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:28.31,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}金色に煌めく 夕暮れる空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:34.02,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}波打ち際どこまでも染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:40.12,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}廻りだす季節の かけらを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:45.60,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そっと触れた指先に感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:50.95,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}あふれる光の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:57.49,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}追逐着 白色帽子的笑声 响彻云际
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:09.03,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}倾听着 过早到来的 夏日之声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:16.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}慢慢地 拉长的两个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:22.00,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}细碎的 脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:28.31,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}夕阳西下的天空 闪烁着耀眼的金色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:34.02,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}映照在波浪间染遍全城
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:40.12,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}细心收集不断变换的 季节的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:45.60,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}蓦然掠过指尖的感触
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:50.95,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}消失在泛起的光芒中


